@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_tauibi(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = tmp
    v1 = ((wp.cos(v1 + 0.13) - (v0 + 0.26 * v1 + 0.50)) * wp.cos(wp.exp(v0 + 0.88)))
    tmp = 0.93
    v2 = 0.49
    v0 = (wp.sin((v1 + 0.69 * v2 + 0.64)) * ((tmp + 0.04 - v1 + 0.55) * wp.sin(v2 + 0.22)))
    data[tid] = v0
